          },
          "author": "Nic Savage",
          "title": "Heartbreak as cricketer commits cardinal sin",
          "description": "Is there a worse feeling in cricket?",
          "url": "https://www.news.com.au/sport/cricket/queensland-paceman-mark-steketee-cruelly-denied-sheffield-shield-hattrick/news-story/53098c9b422030e77278bb07811e8a5e",
